These is the install file for the Wikibase Client extension.

Extension page on mediawiki.org: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Wikibase_Client
Latest version of the install file: https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/r/gitweb?p=mediawiki/extensions/WikidataClient.git;a=blob;f=INSTALL


== Requirements ==

Wikibase Client requires:

* MediaWiki 1.20 or above
* PHP 5.3 or above
* MySQL

== Download ==

TODO

== Installation ==

Once you have downloaded the code, place the ''WikibaseClient'' directory within your MediaWiki 'extensions' directory.
Then add the following code to your [[Manual:LocalSettings.php|LocalSettings.php]] file:

# Wikibase
require_once( "$IP/extensions/WikibaseClient/WikibaseClient.php" );

== Configuration ==

Configuration of Reviews is done by assigning to $egWBCSettings in your
[[Manual:LocalSettings.php|LocalSettings.php]] file, AFTER the inclusion of the
extension. The options are listed below and their default is set in the Wikibase settings file:
https://gerrit.wikimedia.org/r/gitweb?p=mediawiki/extensions/WikidataClient.git;a=blob;f=Wikibase.settings.php
You should NOT modify the settings file, but can have a look at it to get an idea of
how to use the settings, in case the below descriptions do not suffice.

